Pre-release (2 days before the release) 
- Mail translators <gnome-i18n@gnome.org>

Release
- Check that distcheck passes
- Update NEWS with the announcement
- Let the team know so that they can commit last minute fixes
- Add a Changelog entry to each ChangeLog
- Make distcheck
- Install the tarball
- cvs up to check for new changes
- tag the cvs (cvs tag GST_X_Y_Z)
- upload the tarball to ftp.gnome.org
- mail the announcement to gnome-announce-list & setup-tool-hackers
- add the announcement in gnotices
- update the GNOME software map
- add a release in freshmeat
